---
import { siteConfig } from '../config';
---

<section id="book" class="booking-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="booking-container">
      <!-- Info Side -->
      <div class="info-side">
        <div class="info-graphic">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22c5.523 0 10-4.477 10-10S17.523 2 12 2 2 6.477 2 12s4.477 10 10 10z"></path><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"></path><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"></line></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="bilingual-pair" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
          <h2>New to notarization?</h2>
          <span class="lang-zh" style="font-size: 20px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: -12px; margin-bottom: 16px;">第一次办理公证？</span>
        </div>
        <p>Think of a notary as an impartial witness. We verify your identity, ensure you are signing willingly, and observe the signing of your document. <strong>Do not sign your document before we meet.</strong></p>

        <div class="faq-box">
          <h4>
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--brand-terra)" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"></line><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"></line></svg>
            What to bring:
          </h4>
          <ul style="margin-left: 28px; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8;">
            <li>The complete document (unsigned)</li>
            <li>Valid Government-issued ID (Driver's License or Passport)</li>
            <li>Payment (Cash, Venmo, Zelle, or Credit Card)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <a href="#faq" class="btn btn-green" style="margin-top: 32px; align-self: flex-start;">
          Read Notary FAQ
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Calendar Side — Coming Soon -->
      <div class="calendar-side">
        <div class="bilingual-pair" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
          <h3 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600;">Select a day</h3>
          <span class="lang-zh">选择日期</span>
        </div>

        <div class="coming-soon-placeholder">
          <div class="icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--brand-green)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"></line><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"></line><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Coming Soon</h3>
          <p class="lang-zh" style="font-size: 18px; color: var(--brand-green);">即将开放</p>
          <p>Online scheduling will be available once our notary commission is active. Please check back soon!</p>
          <p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted);">
            预约系统将在公证执照生效后开放，请稍后再来！
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
